                <div class="entry-body">		
                    <br><br> <h3 class="title"><a href="">Introduction</a></h3><br>
                    <p align="justify">
                        In the corporate world, polite behaviour and effective presentation hold an importance, as much as knowledge and skills. This session focuses on grooming and etiquette skills which will help the participants to increase their professional image, poise and confidence. This includes a four-course dinner tutorial guaranteed to heighten the students' dining skills as well as an illuminative session on professional grooming which will significantly change the impact that one has in any formal, professional or social situation. 

                        These sessions with a greater concentration on grooming and etiquette skills will help the participants to create the charismatic professional personality that will take them that extra length. 

                    </p>

                    <br> <h3 class="title"><a href="">Content</a></h3><br>

                    <ul>



                        <li>• This program focuses on the customs and rules of polite behaviour at professional standards. </li>
                        <li>• The hands-on workshop consists of sessions targeting professional grooming and dining etiquette.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <br><br/>
                    <br> <h4>Date</h4>30th of December 2013<br>
                    <br> <h4>Time</h4>5:30 PM<br>
                    <br> <h4>Place</h4>Galadari Hotel, Colombo<br>
                    <br> <h4>Speakers</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Mrs. Manusha Weerakkody</li>
                    </ul>
                    <br>




                </div><!--/ .entry-body-->

            </div><!--/ .columns-->

